---
import ArrowDown from '../../../shared/components/icons/ArrowDown';
import DownloadCv from '../../../shared/components/buttons/DownLoadCv';
---

<section class="hero-section relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-visible">
  <div id="hero-content" class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="hero-subtitle mb-6 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-600 dark:text-slate-200 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
        Full Stack Developer
      </span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="hero-title text-7xl sm:text-8xl md:text-9xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-slate-50 leading-[0.92] tracking-tight mb-8 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      David<br/>Phillips
    </h1>
    
    <p class="hero-desc text-xl sm:text-2xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-slate-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-12 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
      Construyo productos web rápidos y pulidos que combinan buen diseño con código robusto.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
      <a 
        href="#projects" 
        class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-neutral-900 dark:bg-slate-100 text-white dark:text-neutral-900 font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] shadow-xl shadow-neutral-900/10 dark:shadow-slate-100/10"
      >
        <span>Ver proyectos</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <DownloadCv />
    </div>
  </div>

  <a 
    href="#experience" 
    id="hero-arrow"
    class="hero-arrow absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-neutral-700 dark:text-slate-200 hover:text-neutral-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors opacity-0 animate-fade-in delay-500"
  >
    <ArrowDown />
  </a>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }

  .delay-100 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .delay-300 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .delay-500 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

  /* Landscape / short viewport adjustments */
  @media (max-height: 550px) {
    .hero-section {
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 5rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-arrow {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>

